            "body": "I stand corrected. https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/sqlite3 -- it is possible, I was misled by http://stackoverflow.com/questions/7784471/using-sqlite3-on-heroku-cedar-stack.\n\nTo get it working all I needed to do was move my database file out of /tmp/ into my root directory. Credit for thorough documentation to https://github.com/mjhea0/flaskr-tdd/blob/master/app.py. Now my issue just falls into the other issues that mention a more thorough example.\n"
